featured_reviews.review_id: We may call this inaddition to masjide.kulsum as ek-minar nalgonda masjid. The masjid is facilitated with desert coolers in summer the ppl who will feel cool while they offer namaz. The mouzzan will give azan exactly the time synchronises with electronic clock. During the ramazan the minar will b decorated with colored bulbs and it is must to watch. The peshimam saheb is nice gentlman who moves friendly with all the ppl and clears doubts abt the islamic culture. Every day lot of children will get deeni taalim under the teaching of peshimam saheb. A big function each year after the completion of summer camp is being organised by youngmen of the mohalla and wll b chaired by none other than our respected Ehsanuddin saheb. Certificates with gifts to the children will b distributed yearly with tasty nonveg food after namaze zoher. We cannot forgot janab S A R Ansari saheb who gifted the masjid for us and some percentage of the savaab gained by the namazis will b credited to sir ansari saheb. Taa.hayath we cannot forgot ansari saheb and special credit goes to janab Ajaz ansari saheb who is dedicating his valuabl time for maintaining the masajids which his father constructed.
